    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The predicted worst-case operating point (6 L/min at 3500 RPM, RHI = 0.87) satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated context of use.",
